# Icons: Use Lucide React

When building UI that needs icons, always use `lucide-react` instead of hand-drawn SVGs or unicode symbols.

```tsx
import { Search, X, Sun, Moon, Crosshair } from 'lucide-react';

<Search size={14} />
<X size={12} />
```

- Already installed as a dependency
- Use `size` prop to control dimensions
- Use `strokeWidth` for weight adjustments (default 2)
- Use `color` or inherit via CSS `currentColor`
